    body
        header.bg-light.rounded-lg
            .container
                h3 勇敢地去追求自己想要的幸福
                h1 向日葵
        section.intro
            .container
                .row
                    .col-md-12
                        h2.section-heading 因花序隨太陽轉動（太陽花）而得名。
                        h3.section-subheading.text-muted  花語為太陽。
                    
                .row
                    .col-md-4.col-sunflower
                        img(src="https://png.pngtree.com/thumb_back/fw800/background/20230804/pngtree-a-beautiful-sunflower-image_12963309.jpg")
                        h4 向日葵總是面向陽光
                        h6.text-muted 象徵著活力和希望
                    .col-md-4.col-sunflower
                        img(src="https://png.pngtree.com/thumb_back/fw800/background/20230804/pngtree-a-beautiful-sunflower-image_12963309.jpg")
                        h4 向日葵總是面向陽光
